{"serial": "94029", "department_serial": 39, "code": "MT7001", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Talent Optimization Program", "ch": "企業優質人才學用培育課程"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Huang, Cheng-Tsu"], "ch": ["黃承祖"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["6", "7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "114"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 60, "department": {"ch": "管理學院", "en": "School of Management"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 56, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程是一門專為管理學院學生設計。課程結合理論與實務，結合企業資源，以104人力銀行線上職涯服務和實體的Giver服務，讓學生從瞭解自己、認識職場、培養能力、職場實作、求職技巧到企業邀約媒合，為一站式的課程設計，是適性揚才的職涯教育訓練課程。 本課程之教學目標如下： 1.以實習或正職為目標的學習：協助學生認清自身求職目標，確認適性的職務內容，並培養良好的工作態度和職場倫理概念。 2.培育即戰力的授課內容，區分為四大類別: 職場探索、職場技能、企業職能、求職技能等一系列嚴謹課程。 3.學校與企業間之共創課程：課程將由業師、學校及104共同討論適合學生之課程，並於期末進行產學專案研究，以實踐大學社會責任、善盡企業社會責任。 4.修課並完成課程同學，有優先參與104人力銀行為本課程所媒合企業之實習機會。", "en": "This course is designed for SOM students utilizing 104 Job Bank’s online services and offline interactions combining theory and practice. It is a one-stop course design, which is a suitable career training course for talent development with corporate resources in helping students understand themselves and the workplace, cultivate their abilities, practice in the workplace, and apply for jobs. The teaching goals of this course are as follows: 1. Provide intern or full-time job oriented learning: assist students to recognize their job goals and appropriate job content, and cultivate a good working attitude and workplace ethics concepts. 2. Cultivating immediate combat power: The course offers a series of well-designed content which can be divided into four domains: workplace exploration, workplace skills, corporate functions, and job search skills. 3. Build up school-industry collaborative courses: The courses will be jointly discussed by teachers, schools and 104 and conduct research project at the end of the semester as to fulfill the goal of university social responsibilities and corporate social responsibilities. 4. Match students for internship opportunities: Students who have taken and completed the course will have priority to participate in the internship or full-time job opportunity of the matching company in the course."}, "outline": {"ch": "以課程第一天的說明為主（以下僅供參考）\nW01 職場探索：課程說明/職涯探索工作坊 (上)\nW02 職場探索：職場實習常見勞資爭議法律實務\nW03 職場探索：職涯探索工作坊 (下)\nW04 職場技能：數位力_數位行銷與社群運用\nW05 企業職能：管理顧問業_勤業眾信(風險諮詢服務)\nW06 企業職能：資訊科技_LINE Taiwan\nW07 求職技能：如何撰寫履歷＆準備面試(線上自主學習)\nW08 企業職能：金融業_永豐銀行\nW09 企業職能：服飾零售業_Uniqlo\nW10 企業職能：零售業_IKEA\nW11 職場技能：專案管理思維\nW12 職場技能：簡報提案技巧(1)：課程講解實作\nW13 求職技能：履歷面試及期末報告準備(自主學習）\nW14 職場技能：簡報提案技巧(2)：期末報告演練\nW15 求職技能：一對一模擬面試\nW16 期末發表會：分組專案提報", "en": "W01 Workplace Exploration: Introduction ＆ Career Exploration Workshop (Part 1)\nW02 Workplace Exploration: Common Labor Disputes Legal Practices in Workplace\nW03 Workplace Exploration: Career Exploration Workshop (Part 2)\nW04 Workplace Skills: Digital Power\nW05 Corporate Lecture：Consulting Industry_Diloitte\nW06 Corporate Lecture：Information Technology_Line Taiwan\nW07 Job hunting skills: How to Write a Resume and Prepare for Interview\nW08 Corporate Lecture：Finance Industry _SinoPac\nW09 Corporate Lecture：Clothing Retail Industry_Uniqlo\nW09 Corporate Lecture：Retail Industry_IKEA\nW11 Workplace Skills: Project Management\nW12 Workplace Skills: Presentation and Proposal Skills（1）\nW13 Job hunting skills: Final Report Rehearsal\nW14 Workplace Skills: Presentation and Proposal Skills（2）\nW15 Job hunting skills: Interview Simulation\nW16 Final report group project report + internship match"}, "textbook": {"ch": "自編教材", "en": "Handouts"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "100", "en": "100"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討\n\n\n其他", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar", "", "", "Others"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "▲指定作業 20％ 。 \n▲課程參與 20％ 。 \n▲期末報告 30％ 。 \n▲課